====Perfective verbs====
The verb [[читать]] does not have corresponding perfective verb, but there are many perfective verbs for [[читать]], formed with prefixes, e.g.:

*[[вычитать|вы́читать]] (''pf'') – to find (smth. by reading); don’t confuse with [[вычитать|вычита́ть]] (''impf'') - to subtract
*[[дочитать]] (''pf'') – to finish reading
*[[зачитать]] (''pf'') – to read out
*[[начитать]] (''pf'') – to read to smb.
*[[почитать]] (''pf'') – to read a little
*[[отчитать]] (''pf'') – to tell off
*[[перечитать]] (''pf'') – to reread, to read again
*[[причитать]] (''pf'') – to lament
*[[прочитать]] (''pf'') – to finish reading
*[[считать]] (''pf'') – to finish reading; don’t confuse with [[считать]] (''impf'') – to count

====Verbal nouns====
Although [[читание]] and [[читка]] are verbal nouns formed from [[читать]], they are very rarely used. For the noun that represents reading as an action, see [[чтение]] (the verbal noun from [[чтить]]).

